  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the transport vehicle, see <a href=\"/index.php/Chariot\" title=\"Chariot\">chariot</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\"><img alt=\"YunkaiHarpie.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/18/YunkaiHarpie.png/50px-YunkaiHarpie.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/18/YunkaiHarpie.png/75px-YunkaiHarpie.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/18/YunkaiHarpie.png/100px-YunkaiHarpie.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Charioteer</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\"><img alt=\"YunkaiHarpie.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/18/YunkaiHarpie.png/50px-YunkaiHarpie.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/18/YunkaiHarpie.png/75px-YunkaiHarpie.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/18/YunkaiHarpie.png/100px-YunkaiHarpie.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Wise_Masters\" title=\"Wise Masters\">Wise Masters</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ghiscari\" title=\"Ghiscari\">Ghiscari</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>The Charioteer</b> is a name the <a href=\"/index.php/Windblown\" title=\"Windblown\">Windblown</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Sellsword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sellsword\">sellsword</a> company hired by <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai</a>, mockingly gave to a <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Yunkish\">Yunkish</a> nobleman commanding some of the Yunkish <a href=\"/index.php/Slave\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slave\">slave</a> solders.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Charioteer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_25\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 25\">Chapter 25</a>, The Windblown.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403153208\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.074 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.261 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 421/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 103